description: Retrieves the contents of a dataset as presigned URIs.

parameters.name: datasetName
parameters.description: The name of the dataset whose contents are retrieved.

nested_items.name: entryName
nested_items.description: The name of the dataset item.

nested_items.name: dataURI
nested_items.description: The presigned URI of the dataset item.

nested_items.name: timestamp
nested_items.description: The time when the request was made.

nested_items.name: state
nested_items.description: The state of the dataset contents. Can be one of READY, CREATING, SUCCEEDED, or FAILED.

nested_items.name: reason
nested_items.description: The reason the dataset contents are in this state.
